    <item>
      <title>美联储选择降息半个百分点，交易员押注进一步宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/traders-bet-on-more-easing-as-fed-opts-for-half-point-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储官员将基准利率下调半个基点、导致短期国债收益率下降后，交易员们加大了对美联储未来宽松步伐的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/traders-bet-on-more-easing-as-fed-opts-for-half-point-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储历史性决定下调基准利率半个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/fed-cuts-benchmark-rate-by-a-half-point-in-historic-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储已下调利率。联邦公开市场委员会以 11 比 1 的投票结果将联邦基金利率下调至 4.75% 至 5% 的区间，此前一年多来，该利率一直维持在 20 年来的最高水平。这并非一致决定。彭博社的 Michael McKee 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/fed-cuts-benchmark-rate-by-a-half-point-in-historic-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:18:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储对股票投资者来说不是一个好的指导</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/fed-is-a-poor-guide-for-stock-investors-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《彭博观点》的 Nir ​​Kaissar 预计，鉴于利率和股价走势相反这一根深蒂固的传统观点，一些投资者会受到追逐股票的诱惑，并表示他们应该重新考虑。他在“彭博市场”节目中与 Sonali Basak 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/fed-is-a-poor-guide-for-stock-investors-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:08:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储自 2020 年以来首次降息后，金价创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/gold-rises-after-us-fed-makes-first-rate-cut-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储周三将基准利率下调半个百分点，金价因此升至历史新高，此举标志着美联储开始积极转变政策以刺激劳动力市场并保护经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/gold-rises-after-us-fed-makes-first-rate-cut-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
